{"type": "article", "id": 12804, "title": "模块化手表", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-30T07:50:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000204xu7fB2PacNTinrsC.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tCovair 为了方便人家快速更换风格，推出了一款模块化的手表。这款表的表面和表带都是可以更换的，而磁铁链接的方式可以让人们迅速的更换，而不需要拆分各种零件。表带有皮革，不锈钢和尼龙三种材质可以选择，而表面也有白色和黑色，数字标示和抽象标示两种。目前产品正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/59168388/covair-interchangeable-watches-with-quick-change-s\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405092KGbz1dAL8FH9fZx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405104dUNhiL6AfwZx1O2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405111pbRjyVIgHTkxOGJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140512DdOn6ZW5ri9aK7Cf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66911765\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140515iTbr45mBGs3nkWzS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66911765\" data-format=\"gif\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405172zG9lbuIkZ5PUS0t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49705882\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261405171GwCqcJP4AXiuRSj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}